'''Polarca VII''' was a small [[Planet/Legends|planet]] located in a neighboring [[Star system/Legends|star system]] &ndash; approximately two hours [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] travel &ndash; to [[Foerost/Legends|Foerost]]. 10,000 kilometers above the surface, [[Station 14]] geosynchronously orbited the world.<ref name="Le facteur X">''{{CasusBelliCite|115|Le facteur X}}''</ref>

